  "title": "API docs, website bootstrap, main expose bootstrap",
  "body": "This is all very WIP but should be a good base to be able to move\nforward with implementing more features.\n\nI tried to create most of the needed widgets we need to implement,\nwithout detailing them most of the time.\n\nTo detail them, have a look at the current instantsearch.js V1 and\nalways take a look at the widget:nameOfWidget label on github so that\nyou better understand what we need to change.\n\nI created some widgets which are direct ripoff searchkit ones because\ntheir naming of ranges is the right one. A range might be by default a\nslider, but not always (think: createRange).\n\nOur next goals should be:\n- implement those widgets with the best API you can think of while being\n  inspired with what exists and the current issues in IS (label:\n  widget:..)\n- continue documenting all widgets and HOC (have a look at\n  createSearchBox and\n  SearchBox documentations to see a complete example)\n- continue bootstraping the website, have a look a site.js\n- HAVE FUN.\n\nI removed the dependencies of the examples/ folder from the main\npackage.json, please create an examples/webpack.config.js and\nexamples/package.json so that we do not bloat the main package.json too\nmuch.\n\nTo start the website: npm start\n",
